results.name: Order of Fibonacci group F(n,4) (or 0 if the group is infinite).
comment: A column of the array described in A202624. See that entry for references.
maple: f:=n-> if n mod 4 = 0 then n-1 elif n mod 4 = 1 then n^4-1 elif n mod 4 = 2 then g((n-2)/4); else 0; fi;
xref: Cf. A202624. A202628 is a subsequence.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 30 2011
